Caster Level(s): Wizard / Sorcerer 6
Innate Level: 6
School: Evocation
Descriptor(s):
Component(s): Verbal, Somatic
Range: Long
Area of Effect / Target: Single
Duration: 3 rounds
Save: Special
Spell Resistance: Yes

A giant hand appears and attempts to bull rush one target. A Fortitude save avoids the spell effects, but failure Dazes target for 3 rounds. The target must also make a reflex save and if that is failed it is knocked down for 1/2 duration ( 9 seconds ).
